	"description": "Hello, everyone! A lot of e-ink has already been spilt on the relatively easier\npickings of “Doing X in React” or “Using React with technology X”. \n\nSo instead, I want to talk about the experiences I&#x27;ve had building frontends\nfrom scratch at DelightChat [https://delightchat.io/] and at my previous\ncompanies.\n\nThese projects require a deeper understanding of React and extended usage in a\nproduction setting.\n\nIf you want to watch a video version of this tutorial to supplement your\nreading, you can",
